<h2>
    Introduction
</h2>
<p>We value your privacy and are committed to protecting the information you share when using our services. This Privacy Policy explains how data is handled and what information is collected during your interactions.</p>

<h2>
    Data Collection
</h2>
<dl>
    <dt>
        No Personal Identifiable Information (PII):
    </dt>
    <dd>
        We do not collect, store, or process personal identifiable data (such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, or other sensitive information) on the server side.
    </dd>
    <dt>
        Interaction Records:
    </dt>
    <dd>
        Interactions with the system may be recorded. These records are strictly used to generate statistical insights about usage patterns.
    </dd>
</dl>
<h2>
    Purpose of Data Usage
</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Improve system performance and reliability</li>

    <li>
        Identify common usage scenarios to enhance user experience
    </li>
    <li>Support research and development for future improvements</li>
</ul>
<h2>
    Data Sharing
</h2>
<p>No personal identifiable data is shared with third parties.</p>
<h2>
    Changes to This Policy
</h2>
<p>This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in practices or legal requirements. Updates will be posted in this document.</p>